The '''Battle of the Angor system''' occurred shortly before the start of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. In the battle, the [[Kyp's Dozen|Dozen and Two Avengers]] under [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Kyp Durron]] attacked [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]' [[Angor system/Legends|Angor system]]. It was believed by the [[New Jedi Order]] that the [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] had ties to [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Fyor Rodan]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], as he used the battle as one of the excuses against giving further benefits to the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].

